00:07:15,791 --> 00:07:16,331
It went live.

135
00:07:17,458 --> 00:07:20,159
We added a lot of features to make kind of a build-up.

136
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:22,801
We added a leveling up system, new game modes,

137
00:07:22,861 --> 00:07:25,603
new characters, and we ended up on the front page of Steam,

138
00:07:25,623 --> 00:07:26,743
which was mind-blowing.

139
00:07:28,044 --> 00:07:29,905
And we also got assigned a Metacritic score.

140
00:07:30,005 --> 00:07:31,106
Now, for those of you who don't know,

141
00:07:31,266 --> 00:07:32,727
Metacritic score is kind of an average

142
00:07:32,967 --> 00:07:34,748
of like some reviews out there.

143
00:07:35,268 --> 00:07:36,609
And in order to get a Metacritic score,

144
00:07:36,649 --> 00:07:38,730
you need a minimum amount of reviews,

145
00:07:38,970 --> 00:07:40,451
and that minimum amount is four,

146
00:07:40,871 --> 00:07:42,372
which is exactly the number we got.

147
00:07:42,532 --> 00:07:44,994
And because most of them were positive,

148
00:07:45,054 --> 00:07:46,034
we ended up with a score of 80.

149
00:07:47,276 --> 00:07:51,677
