00:09:52,446 --> 00:09:55,507
Also, in terms of content, we added, like, new game modes, new characters.

185
00:09:55,908 --> 00:09:57,869
And in terms of online, we added the ability

186
00:09:57,909 --> 00:10:01,070
to join ongoing matches, more local players in online games,

187
00:10:01,190 --> 00:10:01,911
and a friends list.

188
00:10:02,491 --> 00:10:04,112
And in terms of marketing, we managed

189
00:10:04,132 --> 00:10:05,753
to get some announcers for the game,

190
00:10:05,773 --> 00:10:07,714
like the YouTuber Critical, Brutal Muse,

191
00:10:08,014 --> 00:10:09,415
and a random Japanese guy.

192
00:10:10,595 --> 00:10:13,577
And those were quite fun, because these updates kind

193
00:10:13,617 --> 00:10:16,418
of covered all those pillars, not just one.

